=Description=

"Research project by Access Info and the [[Open Knowledge Foundation]], in collaboration with the Open Society Information Program, to map out and evaluate the current state of initiatives to promote access to government data in formats that can be freely used, reused, and distributed by anyone. The project will also identify the obstacles to accessing and reusing public data and recommendations for future initiatives to address these."
(http://opendata-network.org/2010/02/research-the-open-government-data-project/)



